| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5115 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9096b7b1-e8f8-5b10-8f0d-54c111df027b"
